Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.96,0:01:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何我都要问
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.91,0:01:40.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说  法弗尼尔和我们哪个更重要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.97,0:01:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法弗尼尔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.31,0:01:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.96,0:01:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想改变的只有你而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.42,0:02:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.34,0:02:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是对战斗抱有疑问  下一个牺牲者就是你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.77,0:02:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘了羽佐间和甲洋的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.69,0:02:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说这些话是真心的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.03,0:02:24.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所需要的  只是能代替这左眼的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.55,0:02:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第10话  分解～交错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.07,0:02:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作情况怎么样  学姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.57,0:02:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得不错嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.31,0:02:48.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  以后我会更加努力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.34,0:02:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就最好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.28,0:02:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会像羽佐间学姐那么任性的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.18,0:03:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.74,0:03:07.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说羽佐间学姐无视命令破坏了杰克斯号啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.80,0:03:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁说出这种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.53,0:03:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  大家都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.12,0:03:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明什么都不了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.45,0:03:21.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学姐  怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.82,0:03:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.37,0:03:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…在那里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.11,0:03:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.83,0:03:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是不能在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.45,0:03:55.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听到你和皆城的谈话了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.93,0:03:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的左眼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.58,0:04:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.97,0:04:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候  在这里我夺走了他的左眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.93,0:04:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会做出那种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.46,0:04:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望自己至少能代替他的眼睛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.92,0:04:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.16,0:04:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却跟不上他的步子了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.92,0:04:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也难怪  因为他了解外面的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.84,0:04:41.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.34,0:05:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸  你在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.11,0:05:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.92,0:05:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令呢  真壁司令在哪儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.53,0:05:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令  你爸爸正在和皆城开会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.86,0:05:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  叫他过来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.46,0:05:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那时叫我来这里了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.69,0:05:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和总士一起战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.16,0:05:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你是这样对我说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.20,0:06:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总士在外面的世界看到了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.30,0:06:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  关于翔子的传闻太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.23,0:06:20.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很遗憾  有人那么想也是没办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.59,0:06:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子明明保护了岛屿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.33,0:06:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓流言就是那么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.55,0:06:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓子医生  过来一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.35,0:06:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底出了什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.77,0:06:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有个学生呆在广播室里不出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.48,0:06:42.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.75,0:06:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二年级的堂马广登
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.12,0:06:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要老师班级的学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.67,0:06:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是广登的父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.12,0:06:52.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么变成这个样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.23,0:06:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.65,0:06:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为刚才正讨论毕业进路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.40,0:07:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  毕业后他要继承家里的餐厅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.18,0:07:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂马先生  那是关于第二任职的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.60,0:07:13.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的毕业进路讨论是第一任职的志愿调查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.87,0:07:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶员好像不太可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.34,0:07:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  让他在武岛做整备师怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.71,0:07:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各人有各人适合的工作…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.69,0:07:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是做格纳库配置的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.80,0:07:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就我家来说  希望让他在安全的地方工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.39,0:07:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂马  你有什么志愿吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.90,0:07:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以 老实说吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.70,0:07:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.20,0:07:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在东京工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.99,0:07:51.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去东京当明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.46,0:07:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后上音乐节目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.23,0:07:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师来替你决定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.83,0:08:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任职是阿尔比斯地下13层
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.76,0:08:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里我能干什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.59,0:08:07.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗制服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.76,0:08:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.75,0:08:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就这样了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.28,0:08:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看他那样子  广登其实挺纤细的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.67,0:08:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为他设想得不太够啊  要老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.60,0:08:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  以前也发生过同样的事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.15,0:08:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弓子医生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.71,0:08:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是某个想当偶像的人爬上了灯塔吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.18,0:08:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要到东京成为偶像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.23,0:08:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你干过那种事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.59,0:08:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.53,0:08:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂马  快点出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.45,0:08:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和老师们好好谈谈吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.18,0:08:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么好谈的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.43,0:08:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.15,0:09:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我们必须被套在阿卡迪尔计划里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.75,0:09:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.98,0:09:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是堂马？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.24,0:09:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.49,0:09:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  你们不要东张西望  快做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.41,0:09:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的  把我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.88,0:09:29.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的青春还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.77,0:09:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的青春还给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.30,0:09:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  你已经做完了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.46,0:09:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是我出马的时候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.49,0:09:51.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.69,0:09:55.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐头  你知道我的身份吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.37,0:09:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.88,0:10:03.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卫  你可要好好做讲义
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.96,0:10:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑司  不要在走廊上跑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.78,0:10:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么行  我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.47,0:10:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.24,0:10:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.27,0:10:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.70,0:10:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.66,0:10:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事就请交给我这个学生会长吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.98,0:10:28.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  学生会长不是皆城吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.93,0:10:30.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啊  妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.81,0:10:34.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  我也以为是皆城呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.87,0:10:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来总士是学级委员  剑司是学生会长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.24,0:10:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  我也以为是总士呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.32,0:10:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你们啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.85,0:10:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  随你们的便吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.46,0:10:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也不指望你能怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.26,0:11:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂马广登同学  我是学生会长近藤剑司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.31,0:11:07.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛  近藤老师的笨蛋儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.71,0:11:11.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋儿子是什么意思  笨蛋儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.87,0:11:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为人生的学长我要对你说几句
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.63,0:11:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个岛上生存下去就意味着…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.65,0:11:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说  学长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.47,0:11:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听芹说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.48,0:11:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自称用法弗尼尔打倒过菲斯特姆\N这样跟女孩子搭讪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.75,0:11:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.91,0:11:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真差劲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.26,0:11:40.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其实没用法弗尼尔战斗过吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.53,0:11:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也能叫男子汉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.68,0:11:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也用法弗尼尔战斗过啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.24,0:11:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是在模拟练习
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.78,0:11:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁选他做学生会长的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.07,0:11:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为参加侯选的只有剑司一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.47,0:11:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来确实如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.64,0:12:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.46,0:12:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堂马
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.96,0:12:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为你真的能成为明星吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.33,0:12:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事不离开这个岛怎么能知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.96,0:12:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师  老爸  岛上的大人都是骗子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.87,0:12:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗子说的话谁会听
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.64,0:12:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也知道当不了明星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.44,0:12:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.71,0:12:42.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想被困在这岛上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.07,0:12:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得  总觉得被恶鬼包围着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.49,0:12:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次也好  我想看看外面的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.76,0:12:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.64,0:13:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我也有自己想做的事  这有什么不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.14,0:13:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教室里不是写着「希望」两字吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.41,0:13:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很抱歉瞒着你们很多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.79,0:13:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那是为了让你们了解和平的珍贵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.70,0:13:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来这个岛之前  老师们所了解的只有战争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.69,0:13:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有自己想做的事这我们很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.52,0:13:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为老师们没有过这么从容的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.83,0:13:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  那只有在生存下来之后才能做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.60,0:13:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对老师们来说  你们就是希望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.02,0:13:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你们活下去  把岛屿和希望继承下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.37,0:14:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起惊动大家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.75,0:14:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.46,0:14:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,青花鱼  竹荚鱼  沙丁鱼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.26,0:14:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都有哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.47,0:14:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最好吃的是哪种
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.38,0:14:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是哪种  做菜都是上乘的材料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.45,0:14:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.64,0:14:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能做的是哪种呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.05,0:14:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢要做的话  不管哪种都有点勉强啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.85,0:14:46.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  今天跷课了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.77,0:14:48.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事去阿尔比斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.37,0:14:51.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家正准备做晚饭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.41,0:14:53.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.42,0:14:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.06,0:14:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有做饭的心情  今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.13,0:15:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到我家来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.76,0:15:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.94,0:15:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  我来帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.93,0:15:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用不用  你是客人嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.14,0:15:20.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.46,0:15:23.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐  我一辈子的请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.01,0:15:25.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.55,0:15:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.25,0:15:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.05,0:15:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那这个呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.76,0:15:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  把刚才的捞出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.28,0:15:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  为什么把真壁叫来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.07,0:15:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么  不为什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.12,0:15:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起皆城来  我妹妹更喜欢真壁这型啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.00,0:15:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托  不要胡思乱想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.25,0:15:54.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是帮帮忙吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.55,0:15:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用不用  别在意等一会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.38,0:16:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.99,0:16:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟那种事完全没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.92,0:16:07.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.57,0:16:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.91,0:16:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎  后来见到你爸爸了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.66,0:16:18.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.82,0:16:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.88,0:16:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.15,0:16:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑也吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.49,0:16:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.88,0:16:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样  好吃吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.05,0:16:33.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.88,0:16:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  没白努力一场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.85,0:16:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真矢  这鱼丸汤跟我做的味道一模一样嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.76,0:16:49.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的龙宫岛新闻到此结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.52,0:16:52.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来今天的节目稍有变动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.77,0:16:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即将播出特别歌谣节目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.65,0:17:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好  我是堂马广登
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.11,0:17:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.11,0:17:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.00,0:17:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多谢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:27.68,0:17:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.93,0:17:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.84,0:17:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子的传闻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.07,0:17:39.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大致想象得出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.02,0:17:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翔子  还有春日井明明那么拼命地战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.64,0:17:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人怎么说都无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.81,0:17:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会记住他们两人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.52,0:17:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话虽如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.83,0:18:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见会记住我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.21,0:18:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.71,0:18:09.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说一骑也会像翔子那样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.92,0:18:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会  我没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.43,0:18:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.15,0:18:15.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.64,0:18:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕会这样慢慢习惯战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.25,0:18:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得自己好像会变成另一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.46,0:18:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实大家都怀着不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.37,0:18:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天  菲斯特姆来袭击的那天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.69,0:18:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意识到我们曾经相信的一切都是编造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.94,0:18:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许没有人可以做到毫无改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.54,0:18:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我们确实在这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.53,0:18:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是在这里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.86,0:18:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.71,0:19:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.21,0:19:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.21,0:19:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都会记着一骑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.41,0:19:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.21,0:19:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.20,0:19:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.60,0:19:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你脸色不好啊  一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.88,0:19:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  送到这儿就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.03,0:19:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  还是让我妈妈看一下比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.20,0:19:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.98,0:19:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.54,0:19:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想一个人呆一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.69,0:19:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.02,0:20:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后随时来我家吃饭吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.99,0:20:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.31,0:20:10.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.79,0:20:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.24,0:20:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你现在在哪儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.14,0:21:14.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.74,0:21:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.31,0:21:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是精灵号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.65,0:21:22.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.65,0:21:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你下的发射命令吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.52,0:21:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能  不可能下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.72,0:21:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他打算去哪儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.19,0:21:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于离开岛屿的人  我没兴趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.59,0:21:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干得好  真壁一骑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.19,0:21:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪儿  老师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.99,0:21:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的乐园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:59.39,0:22:03.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没有彼此的地方  怎样才能互相理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.10,0:22:05.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们寻求着这个答案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.17,0:22:10.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想找任何借口来掩饰无法理解的事实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.38,0:22:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.21,0:22:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们又再次失去了某样东西

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:26.24,0:23:28.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖弄着旧伤痕的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.07,0:23:32.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的战斗的阴影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.82,0:23:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名为背叛的陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.96,0:23:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回  苍穹的Fafnir  第十一话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.05,0:23:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.74,0:23:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里吗


